r2scan                                macro                               r2scan

NAME
     rr22ssccaann - reflectivity background scans

SYNOPSIS

     rr22ssccaann aallpphhaa__ssttaarrtt aallpphhaa__eenndd aallpphhaa__iinntteerrvvaallss --bbeettaa__ooffff bbeettaa__ooffff
     bbeettaa__iinntteerrvvaallss ttiimmee

DESCRIPTION

     The rr22ssccaann macro runs a series of detector in-plane scans (beta) for
     different angles of incidence (alpha) from aallpphhaa__ssttaarrtt to aallpphhaa__eenndd with
     aallpphhaa__iinntteerrvvaallss. Each scan runs beta from alpha-bbeettaa__ooffff to alpha+bbeettaa__ooffff
     counting for ttiimmee for each of the bbeettaa__iinntteerrvvaallss.

EXAMPLE

     rr22ssccaann 1100mmrr 2200mmrr 1100 --44mmrr 22mmrr 33 11000000

